§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ The ❬projection❭ of $x ∈ 𝗥^n$ onto the subset $S ⊂ 𝗥^n$
    is the point in $S$ closest to $x$. ⦉
⦉

§§ Notation ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ We sometimes the projection of $x$ onto $S$ by $\proj_S(x)$. ⦉

  ‖ We have
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ \proj_S(x) = \argmin_{z ∈ S}{\norm{x - z}} ⦉
    ⦉⦉
⦉

